<title>USA: 3Com unit president Finocchio to resign.</title>
<headline>3Com unit president Finocchio to resign.</headline>
<dateline>SANTA CLARA, Calif. 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>3Com Corp said Monday that Bob Finocchio, president of the 3Com Systems unit, will leave the company for personal reasons.</p>
<p>He will continue with the company in a strategic counsel role and complete his transition out of the company after the end of fiscal 1997 on May 31.</p>
